  "title": "IMMEDIATE WEEKEND ONLY - SAT & SUN; WAREHOUSE SUPPORT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements (FEBRUARY 2026)</strong></p><p>- Warehouse support staff for WEEKENDS (+Public Holiday) : <strong>SATURDAY & SUNDAY </strong><em><strong>(PH - optional)</strong></em></p><p>- Work schedule: <br /><strong>830am to 2.30pm (Saturday)</strong><br /><strong>830am to 1.30pm (Sunday)</strong></p><p>80% of the work is for orders (RedMart) - pick, scan & pack, with about 20% basic warehouse work from stock take, inventory sorting, inbound & outbound handling, etc.  The main focus is on E-Commerce fulfilment & basic computer knowledge is an advantage, but not mandatory.  <br /></p><p>We would like to <u>highlight that some scope of the work is heavy (items from 2kg to 4kg) </u>& there will be need to handle pallets, etc. ; Hence, knowing how to use a pallet jack will be useful (but <u>NOT mandatory</u>); Please also note that 3 warehouses are allocated within the same building - different floors & so, there is a need to move between warehouses for pick & pack operations. </p>",
